00:01:37.760 --> 00:01:40.490
Why did "Star Wars" succeed?

00:01:40.490 --> 00:01:43.190
For those who like
"Star Wars," that's

00:01:43.190 --> 00:01:45.240
not an interesting question.

00:01:45.240 --> 00:01:48.520
I'm hoping that for
