Wars is really about.

00:27:40.390 --> 00:27:43.490
By their innocence and
goodness and by the power

00:27:43.490 --> 00:27:48.320
of their faith and hope,
children redeem their parents.

00:27:48.320 --> 00:27:51.370
As every child wishes
and hopes, any parent

00:27:51.370 --> 00:27:55.380
is likely to save the
child-- risk his life

00:27:55.380 --> 00:27:57.690
to save his child's,
even if it means

00:27:57.690 --> 00:28:00.360
a contest with the
emperor himself.

00:28:00.360 --> 00:28:02.100
And when he does,
the Force is going

00:28:02.100 --> 00:28:04.810
to be right there with him.

00:28:04.810 --> 00:28:08.880
Lawrence Kasdan, very recently
describing his movie career,

00:28:08.880 --> 00:28:12.100
said it's the biggest
adventure you can have,

00:28:12.100 --> 00:28:16.180
