00:45:02.690 --> 00:45:04.185
That's more standard economics.

00:45:06.920 --> 00:45:10.960
That shouldn't change in its
nature, though how it manifests

00:45:10.960 --> 00:45:12.270
itself will change.

00:45:12.270 --> 00:45:15.200
So you can create an
informational cascade

00:45:15.200 --> 00:45:19.240
of the most preposterous
sort in the political domain

00:45:19.240 --> 00:45:23.320
on the internet easily,
whereas pre-internet,

00:45:23.320 --> 00:45:25.060
that was really hard.

00:45:25.060 --> 00:45:27.360
You can create a
reputational cascade

00:45:27.360 --> 00:45:32.060
among a group of, let's
say, "Star Wars" lovers

00:45:32.060 --> 00:45:33.920
easily on the internet.

00:45:33.920 --> 00:45:37.461
So if you say-- I'm a victim
of reputational cascade,

00:45:37.461 --> 00:45:37.960
by the way.

00:45:37.960 --> 00:45:41.720
I've said that the
prequels are under-rated.

00:45:41.720 --> 00:45:43.590
