00:46:33.940 --> 00:46:37.195
I think "The Force Awakens"
is very, very good,

00:46:37.195 --> 00:46:40.610
but "A New Hope" is kind
of world-historically good.

00:46:40.610 --> 00:46:44.090
And the fact that "The Force
Awakens" did so incredibly

00:46:44.090 --> 00:46:49.050
well, it's good network
effects, cascade effects.

