00:55:37.121 --> 00:55:38.870
CASS R. SUNSTEIN: Well,
there's a question

00:55:38.870 --> 00:55:41.310
of individual experience.

00:55:41.310 --> 00:55:45.430
And then, there's a question
of social aggregates.

00:55:45.430 --> 00:55:50.550
So my contention,
which you know is

00:55:50.550 --> 00:55:53.430
based on something
like thick description

00:55:53.430 --> 00:55:56.000
rather than randomized
controlled trial--

00:55:56.000 --> 00:55:57.840
thick description
of the phenomenon

00:55:57.840 --> 00:56:00.000
and how it's been
experienced culturally

00:56:00.000 --> 00:56:04.070
