theme really gets to people.

00:56:04.070 --> 00:56:07.720
And that the twist
on the monomyth,

00:56:07.720 --> 00:56:11.690
about the power of agency, is
something people completely

00:56:11.690 --> 00:56:13.224
resonate to.

00:56:13.224 --> 00:56:18.140
Though it may be for you, it
was the freshness of the images.

00:56:18.140 --> 00:56:21.120
And there's no
question that Lucas'

00:56:21.120 --> 00:56:23.470
spectacular visual
imagination is

00:56:23.470 --> 00:56:28.030
part of the secret sauce
that made this work.

